instructions: PUT THE DINNER PLATE ON THE TABLE
PLACE THE FORK ON THE LEFT OF THE PLATE
PLACE THE SALAD FORK ON NEXT TO THE DINNER FORK
PLACE THE DINNER KNIFE ON THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE PLATE
PLACE THE SALAD KNIFE NEXT TO DINNER KNIFE
KEEP THE SOUP SPOON NEXT TO THE KNIFE'S
KEEP THE WATER GLASS ON THE RIGHT CORNER OF THE PLATE
KEEP THE WINE GLASS NEXT TO WATER GLASS
KEEP EXTRA VWINE GLASS IN THE GLASS ZONE
PLACE THE COFFEE CUP ON THE LAST PLACE WITH SPOON
PLACE THE BREAD PLATE ON THE LEFT TOP OF THE PLATE
KEEP THE BUTTER KNIFE ON THE BREAD PLATE
PLACE THE DESSERT FORK ON THE TOP OF THE PLATE
KEPP THE DESSERT SPOON IN THE OPPOSITE DIRECTION OF FORK
FOR WIPING PLACE THE NAPKIN ON THE PLATE
